  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="ENG">Ukraine: Peace building and conflict monitoring</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="ENG">This project supports local peacemakers and community leaders to address immediate (psychological) needs of their communities and to decrease stress level and tensions at refugee centers and humanitarian aid distribution points. The project also contributes to monitoring of weapon-inflicted harm on civilian and religious infrastructure, conflict-pollution risks and wider environmental damage, which feeds into an improved and informed humanitarian response and post-conflict recovery efforts.</narrative>
  </description>
